TABLE-Australia North West Shelf condensate exports to hold steady in December

Commodities 18 minutes ago (Oct 07, 2019 20:20)

TABLE-Australia North West Shelf condensate exports to hold steady in December SINGAPORE, Oct 7 (Reuters) - * Australia's North West Shelf (NWS) condensate exports will hold at four cargoes in December, steady from the previous month, a loading programme showed on Monday Seller Grade Volume Loading date BP (LON: ) NWS cond 650KB Dec 6-10 Chevron (NYSE: ) NWS cond 650KB Dec 13-17 BHP NWS cond 650KB Dec 20-24 Shell (LON: ) NWS cond 650KB Dec 28-Jan 1
